room_title: Escape room "The Blind Pig Speakeasy" by Granite State Escape in Manchester
room_description:
Your moonshine business has been the talk of the town! Every speakeasy, politician, and millionaire comes to YOU. Until, that is, a competitor comes into town and steals your piece of the pie. So, what are you going to do about it? Just “play nice” in the roaring 20s? I don’t think so…

Infiltrate their establishment, damage their shipment, and steal THEIR client list. This is war, and it’s your move.
